channel.title: Slightley experienced coder looking for project
channel.description:
Hello, I'm Cdoggy.
I have been working on Mopar servers for almost a year. I'm experienced in beginner java, and looking for an experienced coder who is willing to teach me some things for my help.
I can do simple things from: Make a simple Grading Program, with java. To making a GUI or Graphical User Interface. ~~~ Need a project with a fun attitude, the worst thing to do is to get too serious and get bored.
Thanks Cdoggy.
P.S. Email me at cdoggy12@hotmail.com if you would like to contact me, or post here.
